title: Gyros and Kebobs
typeOfFood: Mediterranean, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Greek, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Counter service Americanized Greek style food: falafel, hummus, pita bread. Saffron rice, onion rings, and french fries supposed to vegan (ask if has separate fryer). Sauce on falafel is not vegan - vegans to ask for a different sauce. Will accommodate.
